1	Hello
2	World
--- url('file://<relative>') resolves under user_files ---
1	Hello
2	World
--- format auto-detected from the .csv extension ---
2
--- url_base routes a relative reference to the File engine ---
1	Hello
2	World
--- CREATE TABLE ... ENGINE = URL('file://...') reads via the File engine ---
1	Hello
2	World
--- INSERT INTO url('file://...') round-trips through the File engine ---
3	Three
--- reading outside user_files via a relative file:// path is rejected ---
rejected
